# Star Wars API Client (Python)

This project is a Python script that fetches and displays data from the Star Wars API (SWAPI).

## Features

* Fetches Star Wars character data
* Handles API requests using Python
* Parses and displays JSON responses

## Tech Stack

* Python
* requests
* REST API (SWAPI)

## How to Run

```bash
pip install requests
python main.py
```

## Example Output

Displays Star Wars character or film data directly in the console.
